quran[40]{c,v,t}:
  77,1,O woondirii keneeli dewandir…ói hono siiru puccu
  77,2,E bippooji bippugol
  77,3,E carooji cargolo
  77,4,E ceerndooji ceerndugol
  77,5,E tellinooji wahyu
  77,6,Gantingol wollo jeertingol
  77,7,"ko podante …óon ko, ko goongo"
  77,8,Si koode …óe momtaama
  77,9,Si kammu o huuftaama
  77,10,Si pelle …óe nawaama
  77,11,Saanga Nelaa…ìe kappana waktu
  77,12,E √±alawma dirtinaa…óo
  77,13,Wonande √±alngu ceerndugol
  77,14,Holko anndin ma √±alngu ceerndugol
  77,15,"haray nden √±alnde, bone woodanii fennu…ìe …ìen"
  77,16,Mbela Min kalkaani adinoo…ìe …ìe
  77,17,Refti Min ndewni heen sakkatii…ìe …ìe
  77,18,Ko hono nih Min mba…óata bon…ìe …ìe
  77,19,"haray nden √±alnde, bone woodanii fennu…ìe …ìen"
  77,20,Mbela Min tagaani mon e ndiyam koy…óam
  77,21,Min mba…ói …óam e rannga hu…ìandiinga
  77,22,Haa e happu ganndaa…óo
  77,23,Min koddiri mbo heskey …ìe Hoddiroo…ìe
  77,24,"haray nden √±alnde, bone woodanii fennu…ìe …ìen"
  77,25,Mbela Min mba…óaani leydi coomoori mon
  77,26,Wuur…ìe e maay…ìe
  77,27,Min mba…ói e hendi pen…óe toow…óe Min njarni mon ndiyam mbel…óam
  77,28,"haray nden √±alnde, bone woodanii fennu…ìe …ìen"
  77,29,Pokkitane faade ko pennatna…óon
  77,30,Pokkitane faade e …óowdi ndi …óem…óe tati
  77,31,Ndi …óowdintah nafatah e lew lewndu
  77,32,Honge werlo peete mawe hono ku…ìeeje
  77,33,Elle ko…óe geloobi coooyi
  77,34,"haray nden √±alnde, bone woodanii fennu…ìe …ìen"
  77,35,E o √±alngu …ìe kaalatah
  77,36,∆Åe cakkittaake saba …ìe ngantina
  77,37,"haray nden √±alnde, bone woodanii fennu…ìe …ìen"
  77,38,O ko √±alngu ceerndugol Min ndenndinii on wondude e adii…ìe …ìe
  77,39,Si tawii ho…óon njogii feere pewjanee kam
  77,40,"haray nden √±alnde, bone woodanii fennu…ìe …ìen"